item.title: Build Laravel 9 API - Build CRUD | #1 How to Install Laravel 9 in Windows
item.description: We will start to build API project using Laravel 9, and in this article we will learn how to install laravel 9 in easy way. In this project, we will install Laravel using Laragon. We also will learn how to upload images in API using laravel 9, and simulate the data using API. We use windows 10 to build this project. 1 - Install Git CLI Download and install git from here: https://git-scm.
